{"tid":2022770,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"光復香港 時代革命","createTime":"2020-05-18T13:41:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T13:56:45.000Z","uid":252659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7f32807846a653077eb40bea0bb19512f7d67d34","tid":2022770,"uid":252659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T13:41:52.000Z","msg":"有邊個唔想贏?<br />\n<br />\n但照個勢咁睇, 想贏都幾難 <br />\n香港人廢老無非一個心態<br />\n就係等人餵 等人救<br />\n輕鬆慣, 做慣經紀<br />\n好聽啲就叫超級中介人, 唔好聽就叫condom<br />\n咩都望大陸放水畀你<br />\n大陸唔放你 就求外國 <br />\n最多就叫口號 當抗爭 <br />\n李慧琼 都講到明叫你有本事去法庭告佢<br />\n根本係終極嘅侮辱 <br />\n勇武派同班靚仔衰極都叫靠自己 <br />\n有咩唔完善 衰極都叫靠自己雙手 <br />\n泛民主真係含得撚啦<br />\n你想做嘅角色<br />\n田北辰已經幫你日做夜做<br />\n慳番啖氣啦"},{"pid":"265efac73697970d21c7c0ad3b21d73594e0dc5c","tid":2022770,"uid":12773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T13:45:56.000Z","msg":"Sad but true<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cf3532fb9ab1cbd6f7289d0db1dab9027b62d79","tid":2022770,"uid":252659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"265efac73697970d21c7c0ad3b21d73594e0dc5c","tid":2022770,"uid":12773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T13:45:56.000Z","msg":"Sad but true<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T13:56:45.000Z","msg":"可惜廢老未明<br />\n開口埋口佩洛西<br />\n扯曬旗咁"}]}